Subject: [PATCH 29/75] runtime/cgo: add cgo function call support for loong64

Change-Id: I8ef0e7f17d6ada3d2f07c81524136b78457e7795
---
 src/runtime/cgo/asm_loong64.s       | 69 +++++++++++++++++++++++++
 src/runtime/cgo/gcc_linux_loong64.c | 78 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
 src/runtime/cgo/gcc_loong64.S       | 67 +++++++++++++++++++++++++
 3 files changed, 214 insertions(+)
